Class Version

java.lang.Object
com.insebre.project.model.Version
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Version extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a version of a software program. Each version has a version number, release date, and associated commits.

      date - The release date of the version (e.g., "2024-05-10").
      commits - A description of the commits included in this version.
